On Experience gain...
  Get the enemy
  Get the amount of Experience

  Get the player's max xp
  Get the player's current xp

  Update the player's max xp
  Update the player's current xp

  Does the enemy exist in the cache?
    If so, is it yielding less more or the same this time? (Display in message)
    If not, create an entry

  Record this event
    Does a previous record exist?
      If so, calculate how much xp was calculated over this time (currentTime - lastTime) / (lastYield + currentYield)

  Calculate amount of {enemy} required to level up = ((max - current) / yield)
